 We Learn Luke Skywalker's Stance on Trade Federations and Embargoes? #StarWars *(20:58:00)** Star Wars: The Force Awakens Official Teaser #2 just Jumping on the #starwars Bandwagon, Fuck Yea! https://t.co/ygeR72CCM7 *(21:03:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Twitter Mentions* @doghousemike Can I Join In? #dnd #rumtimes. *(Mentioned by RubiconTom)* *(17:51:00)** @doghousemike More like Lots of Drunk Reading to Do!!! #rumtastic #shotgunmage. *(Mentioned by RubiconTom)* *(18:11:00)** @doghousemike just Saying I Wanna Be a Mage before Anyone Else ;) #frostmage #frostbolt. *(Mentioned by RubiconTom)* *(18:13:00)** @doghousemike Its a Good Bandwagon to Be On.. *(Mentioned by DarrenWhiting)* *(21:05:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>","lines":[13,14],"size":2971,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
